sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    Note over browser: User writes a new note in the SPA input field and clicks Save

    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa<br/>JSON payload with note content + timestamp
    activate server
    server-->>browser: 201 Created (JSON confirmation)
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: SPA updates the UI dynamically without reloading the page

    Note right of browser: The new note is added to browser's in-memory list<br/>and rendered immediately
